===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 63 people, 29 households, and 21 families residing in the city. The [[population density]] was 497.8 inhabitants per square mile (192.2/km<sup>2</sup>). Housing unit density was 252.9 per square mile (97.6/km<sup>2</sup>). The median age was 55.5 years. 17.5% of residents were under the age of 18 and 30.2% were 65 years of age or older. For every 100 females, there were 125.0 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over, there were 136.4 males.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A33240&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A33240&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A33240&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

Of all households, 37.9% had children under the age of 18 living with them, 41.4% were married-couple households, 3.4% were cohabiting-couple households, 37.9% were households with a female householder and no spouse or partner present, and 17.2% were households with a male householder and no spouse or partner present. 27.6% of all households were non-families. About 20.6% of all households were made up of individuals, and 10.3% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

There were 32 housing units, of which 9.4% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 28.6%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The age distribution was 19.0% under the age of 20, 1.6% from 20 to 24, 20.6% from 25 to 44, and 28.6% from 45 to 64. The gender makeup of the city was 55.6% male and 44.4% female.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

